(43, 13, 26, 42, 22, 21, 21, NULL, 'Betrayal at the Table', 'Both passages emphasize the presence of Judas at the table during the Last Supper. John specifies that Jesus gives a sop to Judas, while Luke notes that the betrayer''s hand is with Jesus on the table.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
